=== 返回英倫求學 ===
華德斯退休後考入[[羅浮堡大學|羅浮堡大學]]教育學系。他於1982年獲[[哲學碩士|哲學碩士]]學位，並於1985年獲[[哲學博士|哲學博士]]學位。華德斯的碩士論文題為《The technical institutes in Hong Kong 1969 to 1980: A study of their development》（1969年至1980年間的香港工業學院：發展研究論文）<ref>{{Cite thesis |last=Waters |first=Deric D. |date=1982-01-01 |title=The technical institutes in Hong Kong 1969 to 1980: A study of their development |type=MPhil |publisher=Loughborough University |url=https://repository.lboro.ac.uk/articles/thesis/The_technical_institutes_in_Hong_Kong_1969_to_1980_a_study_of_their_development/9333416 |access-date=2021-03-16 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128100124/https://repository.lboro.ac.uk/articles/thesis/The_technical_institutes_in_Hong_Kong_1969_to_1980_a_study_of_their_development/9333416 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他的博士論文題為《The planning of craft and technician education in Hong Kong 1957 to 1982》（1957年至1982年香港的手藝及工業教育計劃）<ref>{{Cite thesis |last=Waters |first=Deric D. |date=1985-01-01 |title=The planning of craft and technician education in Hong Kong 1957 to 1982 |type=PhD |publisher=Loughborough University |url=https://repository.lboro.ac.uk/articles/thesis/The_planning_of_craft_and_technician_education_in_Hong_Kong_1957_to_1982/9333167 |access-date=2021-03-16 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128100044/https://repository.lboro.ac.uk/articles/thesis/The_planning_of_craft_and_technician_education_in_Hong_Kong_1957_to_1982/9333167 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 古蹟保育工作 ===
華德斯於1990年至1998年間擔任[[古物諮詢委員會|古物諮詢委員會]]委員<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Membership of the Antiquities Advisory Board 1997-98 |url=https://www.amo.gov.hk/form/newsletter_199807.pdf |date=1998-07 |journal=Heritage Hong Kong |issue=1 |volume=2 |page=31 |access-date=2021-03-16 |archive-date=2019-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191023224128/http://www.amo.gov.hk/form/newsletter_199807.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1998年，時任[[香港特別行政區行政長官|香港特別行政區行政長官]][[董建華|董建華]]向華德斯頒發[[銅紫荊星章|銅紫荊星章]]，以表揚他對香港古蹟保育的貢獻及在古物諮詢委員會的傑出服務<ref>{{Cite web |title=1998 Honours List |url=https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/199807/01/0630215.htm |date=1998-07-01 |publisher=HKSAR Government Press Release |website=Daily Information Bulletin |access-date=2021-03-16 |archive-date=2001-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20010715103514/http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/199807/01/0630215.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[油麻地天后廟|油麻地天后廟]]於2020年被定為[[香港法定古蹟列表|香港法定古蹟]]，發展局在提交給立法會的文件中引用了華德斯1999年的著作《The Temples off Public Square Street》<ref>{{Cite web |title=立法會參考資料摘要《古物及古蹟條例》(第 53 章)《2020 年古物及古蹟(古蹟及歷史建築物的宣布)(綜合)(修訂)公告》 |url=https://www.heritage.gov.hk/tc/doc/LegCo_Brief_Antiquities_and_Monuments_Declaration_of_Monuments_and_Historical_Buildings_Consolidation_Amendment_2020_TC.pdf |accessdate=2021-03-16 |author=發展局 |date=2020-05-22 |publisher=立法會 |archive-date=2021-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316171630/https://www.heritage.gov.hk/tc/doc/LegCo_Brief_Antiquities_and_Monuments_Declaration_of_Monuments_and_Historical_Buildings_Consolidation_Amendment_2020_TC.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 個人生活與逝世 ==
華德斯與陳麗冰（{{lang|en|Vera Chan Lai-hing}}）在1960年4月21日於[[聖安多尼堂_(香港)|聖安多尼堂]]結婚<ref name="scmp">{{Cite news |url=https://www.scmp.com/magazines/post-magazine/article/1702766/60-years-hongkonger-dan-waters-teaching-tiananmen-and |title=60 years a Hongkonger: Dan Waters on the second world war, karate kicks and mixed-marriages |first=Jenni |date=2015-02-07 |work=South China Morning Post |last1=Marsh |access-date=2021-03-16 |archive-date=2019-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191128181111/https://www.scmp.com/magazines/post-magazine/article/1702766/60-years-hongkonger-dan-waters-teaching-tiananmen-and |dead-url=no }}</ref>。陳麗冰曾於[[渣打銀行（香港）|渣打銀行（香港）]]任職經理，於1974年被選為首位女性[[香港十大傑出青年|香港十大傑出青年]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Meeting the Author Night One Couple Two Cultures: 81 Western-Chinese Couples Talk About Love and Marriage / Dan Waters|url=https://lib.hku.hk/friends/reading_club/bt2005_9.html|accessdate=2021-03-16|author=The University of Hong Kong Libraries Reading Club|date=2005-12-15|publisher=The University of Hong Kong|archive-date=2009-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090906113001/http://lib.hku.hk/friends/reading_club/bt2005_9.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她及後亦有華慧娜（{{lang|en|Vera Waters}}）的別稱<ref name="scmp"/>。

運動方面，華德斯在57歲時獲得[[空手道|空手道]]黑帶<ref name="rice lingnan"/><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1907075/deric-daniel-waters-remarkably-fit-man-who-laid-groundwork-hong-kong |title=Deric Daniel Waters: A ‘remarkably fit’ man who laid the groundwork for Hong Kong Polytechnic University |first=Annemarie |date=2016-01-30 |work=South China Morning Post |last1=Evans |access-date=2021-03-16 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108111810/http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1907075/deric-daniel-waters-remarkably-fit-man-who-laid-groundwork-hong-kong |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他亦是香港70歲以上公開組800米及1500米賽跑紀錄保持者<ref name="rice lingnan"/>。

2006年1月，華德斯氏夫婦在皇家亞洲學會香港分會及[[香港公共圖書館|香港公共圖書館]]聯合舉辦的「One couple two cultures : Western-Chinese couples talk about love and marriage」（兩種文化的伴侶：中西伴侶談愛情與婚姻）座談會中主講，內容其後被收錄於「香港口述歷史特藏 - 移民、少數族裔、居港外籍人士」<ref>{{Cite web |title=Hong Kong Oral History Collection -Immigrants, Ethnic minorities & Expatriates |url=https://www.hkpl.gov.hk/en/thematic/ohi/resources/Immigrants.html |publisher=Hong Kong Public Libraries |website=Hong Kong Oral History Resources |access-date=2021-03-16 |archive-date=2018-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181014061126/https://www.hkpl.gov.hk/en/thematic/ohi/resources/Immigrants.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=One couple two cultures : Western-Chinese couples talk about love and marriage |url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJHEQs3LpK2zd |date=2006-01-20 |publisher=Hong Kong Public Libraries |website=Multimedia Information System |access-date=2021-03-16 |archive-date=2018-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181113191401/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJHEQs3LpK2zd |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年1月27日，華德斯於香港逝世，享年94歲<ref name="RASHK" />。[[香港理工大學|香港理工大學]]李嘉誠樓旁的草地有一路燈以華德斯命名，紀念其對香港教育的傑出貢獻<ref>{{Cite web |title=Dr Deric Daniel Waters Birthday Party |url=https://www.polyu.edu.hk/aado/email/AlumNews_20151127.htm |date=2015-11-27 |publisher=PolyU |website=AlumNews@PolyU |access-date=2021-03-16 |archive-date=2016-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827044141/http://www.polyu.edu.hk/aado/email/AlumNews_20151127.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

